OL,3,CMakerfield: Meet the candidates in the
OL,4,CUK's most consequential by-election
OL,6,FWatch: ITV News' Political
OL,7,FCorrespondent Harry Horton visited
OL,8,FMakerfield to find out more about the
OL,9,Fcandidates running in this significant
OL,10,Fby-election.
OL,12,FThe Makerfield by-election could shape
OL,13,Fthe future politics of the entire
OL,14,Fcountry.
OL,16,FVoters across the constituency in
OL,17,Fnorth west England will be well aware
OL,18,Fof the significance of the poll.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
