OL,3,CMakerfield: Meet the candidates in the
OL,4,CUK's most consequential by-election
OL,6,FIt was triggered after the previous
OL,7,FLabour MP, Josh Simons, stood down to
OL,8,Fallow Greater Manchester Mayor Andy
OL,9,FBurnham the opportunity to return to
OL,10,FWestminster.
OL,12,FThere are fourteen candidates
OL,13,Fstanding, and hundreds of MPs,
OL,14,Factivists and journalists have visited
OL,15,Fthe towns of Makerfield in recent
OL,16,Fweeks.
OL,18,FITV News has spoken to candidates from
OL,19,Fthe Conservatives, Green Party,
OL,20,FLabour, Liberal Democrats, and Reform
OL,21,FUK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
