OL,3,CMakerfield: Meet the candidates in the
OL,4,CUK's most consequential by-election
OL,6,FJake Austin
OL,8,FJake Austin is a Liberal Democrat
OL,9,Fcouncillor in Stockport and stood as a
OL,10,Fcandidate in the 2024 Greater
OL,11,FManchester Mayor election.
OL,13,FAndy Burnham
OL,15,FAndy Burnham has been the Greater
OL,16,FManchester Mayor since 2017 and was
OL,17,Fpreviously MP for Leigh. He is widely
OL,18,Fexpected to launch a bid to become
OL,19,Fprime minister if he wins the
OL,20,Fbyelection.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
