OL,3,CMakerfield: Meet the candidates in the
OL,4,CUK's most consequential by-election
OL,6,FRobert Kenyon
OL,8,FRobert Kenyon is a plumber and local
OL,9,Fcouncillor. He was elected to Wigan
OL,10,Fcouncil in May 2026 and stood as
OL,11,FReform UK's candidate in Makerfield at
OL,12,Fthe 2024 general election, finishing
OL,13,Fin second place.
OL,15,FSarah Wakefield
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
