OL,3,CMakerfield: Meet the candidates in the
OL,4,CUK's most consequential by-election
OL,6,FThe Green Party's first candidate
OL,7,Fwithdrew from the contest after
OL,8,Fallegations of historical antisemitic
OL,9,Fsocial media posts emerged. The
OL,10,Fparty's second candidate is Sarah
OL,11,FWinstanley, a councillor in Manchester.
OL,13,FMichael Winstanley
OL,15,FThe Conservative candidate is Michael
OL,16,FWinstanley, a former councillor in
OL,17,FWigan.
OL,19,FThe full list of candidates running in
OL,20,Fthe Makerfield by-election is as
OL,21,Ffollows:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
